71204/photo/bkncn-20171204092141601-1204_05011_001_01p.jpg?20171204110929\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171204%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171204092141601-1204_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20171204110929&h=f138f8f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n內地網絡近日流傳一段男子在車廂被圍毆的短片，事發於上周六（2日）晚上7時20分左右，一名中國人在日本東京JR京濱東北線的火車上，被兩名疑似喝醉的日本人毆打。據指打人者已被當地警方抓獲，而被打傷的中國人不僅面部骨折，更出現腦震盪。有傳打人者是日本右翼人士，惟消息未獲證實。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n從網傳片段所見，兩名日本人在車廂中圍着一名男子，並對他拳打腳踢。被打的男子未有還手，只是以雙手護頭不斷捱打，其後才有警員趕到現場，拉開兩名日本人。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n片段流出後，旋即引起網民討論，有人表示被打的中國人當時看了兩名日本人一眼，結果從西川口至赤羽站兩個站之間被他們瘋狂毆打。亦有網民稱自己曾遇過同一情況，「日本人確實會對一眼不爽就找你麻煩，親身經歷」。惟事發至今，仍未有官方通報事件。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171204/photo/bkncn-20171204092141601-1204_05011_001_02b.jpg?20171204110929\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171204%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171204092141601-1204_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20171204110929&h=45c20474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n日本警員接報到場。（網上圖片）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171204/photo/bkncn-20171204092141601-1204_05011_001_03b.jpg?20171204110929\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171204%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171204092141601-1204_05011_001_03b.jpg%3F20171204110929&h=c4e76153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打人男子被警員拉出車廂後，仍企圖衝回去。</span></span>（網上圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比警察拉走都仲想返去打鳩佢地<br />\n我就唔信件事係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6c7e941eaf4bd3334a3c40a0132f5db5e7d5c4","tid":488970,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:13:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">另有網民指，中國男子在地鐵內玩手機遊戲《王者榮耀》時，望了上車的日本人一眼，即被對方毆打。</span><br />\n我買佢當時開大個喇叭響地鐵打機</blockquote><br />\n所以要打柒佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抵啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本玩支那game仲要開聲玩，抵佢比人打。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條友9up話佢開大聲，你唔好當真先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陣間又想炒車呀</blockquote><br />\n一講到中國，個個連登仔就ff<span style=\"color: red;\">人地周街痾屎，周圍吐啖</span><br />\n<br />\n成班死毒撚個思維去撚晒90年代？</blockquote><br />\n紅字根本係事實 ff乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱放監？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱放監?<br />\n有支那人唔係周街痾屎，周圍吐啖咩?"},{"pid":"4066f4a4412f2e091a49a13db989b11cf08a3927","tid":488970,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:14:13.000Z","msg":"咪又係一車車小支支去大日本掃貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a049c6a4341c077fa4f4de78eee1455a839ffd","tid":488970,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:15:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>京濱東北線幾時變咗地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咁應該叫咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n火車囉, 未見過主線鐵路 (mainline rail) 用1067mm窄軌 1500V dc overhead line? <br />\n通勤化, 通勤型化, 捷運化, 東鐵綫你會問係唔係火車? 你會分日本電車同列車?</blockquote><br />\n日本法律分地鐵同火車好清楚<br />\nJR係火車，唔洗車頭逃生門（香港九鐵都一樣）<br />\n地鐵就係地鐵，隧道細一定要逃生門</blockquote><br />\n呢個再technical啲, 重有鐵道法同軌道法嘅分別"},{"pid":"db3187782fd661c1ada078052966bf76ff2c82c9","tid":488970,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/191530_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F191530_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=7956ecc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2bcbce959c367aa23e9589f32121ca1ab63b007","tid":488970,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/191530_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F191530_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=7956ecc0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你老母2打1，你估個個葉問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa2fad46cb33540fbeec14e28eb521ba38f47e4","tid":488970,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:18:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>京濱東北線幾時變咗地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咁應該叫咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n火車囉, 未見過主線鐵路 (mainline rail) 用1067mm窄軌 1500V dc overhead line? <br />\n通勤化, 通勤型化, 捷運化, 東鐵綫你會問係唔係火車? 你會分日本電車同列車?</blockquote><br />\n日本法律分地鐵同火車好清楚<br />\nJR係火車，唔洗車頭逃生門（香港九鐵都一樣）<br />\n地鐵就係地鐵，隧道細一定要逃生門</blockquote><br />\n呢個再technical啲, 重有鐵道法同軌道法嘅分別</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abc2ad2fc268a9a12b9c6d658c3bba964c9673c","tid":488970,"uid":38997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:20:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.recordchina.co.jp/b225990-s0-c30.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.recordchina.co.jp%2Fb225990-s0-c30.html&d=fvfZ903C9G%2BtEKZ90tb7wwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d715e8e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.recordchina.co.jp/b225990-s0-c30.html</a><br />\n<br />\n加害者が日本人かどうかは分からない。<span style=\"color: red;\">彼らが韓国語を話しているのを聞いたという人もいる。いずれにせよ中国人ではなかった</span>」などと説明しているようだ。また、暴行は加害者2人が乗車した西川口から赤羽まで続いたとも伝えられている。<br />\n<br />\n加害者についてはさまざまな情報が錯綜している。日本のネット上では当初、「外国人同士のトラブル」という情報が出ていた。動画では、<span style=\"color: red;\">暴行を止めようとしている日本人男性が「NO、NO」と英語を使っていること</span>、加害者の一人が発した日本語になまりがあるように聞こえることから、日本人ではないという見方も。さらに、転載された動画を見たユーザーからは「<span style=\"color: red;\">モンゴル語が聞こえた」という証言も出ている模様だ。</span> <br />\n<br />\n點呀，又泡又蒙古語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阻止果條友用英文叫人停架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過拉走仲衝返入去打，肯定好大仇口<br />\n應該有內情"},{"pid":"2a7050d0248f0d5dc88fd23dd0c2e7f00f7d4b83","tid":488970,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:21:06.000Z","msg":"快點反日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我要去日本呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fcd19dd315f7e93ccfdf5c4c8096e2eba60fd9","tid":488970,"uid":18197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:22:36.000Z","msg":"支那人沒有一個是無辜的.jpg"},{"pid":"ff83585c7d0bce2deb198f596034437d25f73899","tid":488970,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快點反日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我要去日本呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無論件事來龍去脈係點，我剩係想反日<br />\n剩係想多啲支那人知道呢件事，激發佢地既民族主義去抵制日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70241281d9c2807ad325cb2df6b042cf402d05d0",